32#ifndef _ASM_DIV64_H_
33#define _ASM_DIV64_H_
34
35#include <sys/types.h>
36
37#define do_div(n_q, d) _do_div(&(n_q), (d))
38
39static inline uint32_t
40_do_div(uint64_t *n_q, uint32_t d)
41{
42 const uint32_t r = *n_q % d;
43 const uint32_t q = *n_q / d;
44
45 *n_q = q;
46 return r;
47}
48
49#endif /* _ASM_DIV64_H_ */
